{
    "comments1":"这是一个储存菜单栏信息的json文件，通过读取它，可以读取一个菜单的信息",

    "comments2":"hudUnits储存这个菜单中所有的元件信息",
    "hudUnits":[
        {
            "name":"SampleName",
            "hudClass":"full_leaf_framework.Interact.Image",
            "drawableInfo":{
                "spriteInfo":{
                    "location":"Map/SampleFolder/SampleSprite",
                    "rows":1,
                    "column":2,
                    "frameDelay":0.2,
                    "startFrame":0
                },
                "posX":50,
                "posY":50,
                "anchorPointX":0,
                "anchorPointY":0,
                "sizeScale":1,
                "angle":0,
                "layer":1
            },
            "collisionBox":[
                {"X":0, "Y":0},
                {"X":100, "Y":0},
                {"X":100, "Y":50},
                {"X":0, "Y":50}
            ],
            "comments3":"每个元件中，元件的名称，类别，绘制对象和碰撞箱的部分必须定义，其他参数使用extArgus传入",
            "extArugs":[]
        }
    ],
    "animationTracks":{
        "locations":[
            "utils/Visual/sample_animation.json"
        ],
        "comments4":"储存在locations数组中的动画轨迹信息会被读取，在接下来可以用到"
    },
    "initialize":[
        {
            "type":"add_event",
            "target":"@a",
            "object":"full_leaf_framework.Interact.Hud.SampleFunction",
            "handler":"idle"
        },
        {
            "type":"add_animation",
            "target":"@a",
            "object":"SampleAniamtion",
            "handler":"current"
        }
    ],
    "comments5":"使用以下的格式指定命令，可以向已有的元件中传递委托绑定事件，添加动画",
    "comments6":"自己搞一个Hud的继承类，在里面写好相应的方法，传递委托的时候会根据方法名称创建相应的委托",
    "commands":[
        {
            "name":"SampleRmvCommand",
            "sequence":[
                {
                    "type":"rmv_event",
                    "target":"@a",
                    "object":"full_leaf_framework.Interact.Hud.SampleFunction",
                    "handler":"idle"
                },
                {
                    "type":"rmv_animation",
                    "target":"@a",
                    "object":"SampleAniamtion",
                    "handler":"current"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}